371  ZIP_SIZE_TYPE LeftBytesToProcess() const {return m_uTotalBytesToProcess - m_uBytesProcessed;}
372  private:
373  void Init(ZIP_SIZE_TYPE uTotalItemsToProcess, ZIP_SIZE_TYPE uTotalBytesToProcess, int iReactType)
374  {
375  m_uTotalFilesToProcess = uTotalItemsToProcess;
376  m_uTotalBytesToProcess = uTotalBytesToProcess;
377  m_uBytesProcessed = m_uFilesProcessed = 0;
378  m_iReactType = iReactType;
379  m_bActive = false;
380  }
381  void OnCallbackInit(int iType)
382  {
383  // this assumes, that the callback type will stay unchanged
384  // between Init() and CallbackEnd()
385  m_bActive = iType == m_iReactType;
386  }
387 
388  void OnCallCallback(ZIP_SIZE_TYPE uProgress)
389  {
390  if (m_bActive)
391  m_uBytesProcessed += uProgress;
392  }
393  bool OnNextFile()
394  {
395  if (m_bActive)
396  {
397  m_uFilesProcessed++;
398  return true;
399  }
400  else
401  return false;
402  }
403  bool m_bActive;
404  int m_iReactType;
405  };

601  virtual int GetStepSize()
602  {
603  return m_iType == cbSave || m_iType == cbDeleteCnt || m_iType == cbCalculateForMulti || m_iType == cbEncryptPrepare ? 256 : 1;

621  bool RequestCallback(ZIP_SIZE_TYPE uProgress = 1)
622  {
623  if (!uProgress)
624  return true;
625  if (m_iCachedStepSize == 1)
626  return CallCallback(uProgress);
627  else
628  {
629  m_uAccumulatedProgress += uProgress;
630  if (m_iCurrentStep >= m_iCachedStepSize)
631  {
632  bool ret = CallCallback(m_uAccumulatedProgress);
633  ResetProgressStage();
634  return ret;
635  }
636  else
637  {
638  m_iCurrentStep++;
639  return true;
640  }
641  }
642  }
643 
657  bool RequestLastCallback(ZIP_SIZE_TYPE uProgress = 0)
658  {
659  bool ret;
660  if (m_uAccumulatedProgress == 0 && uProgress == 0)
661  ret = true;
662  else
663  ret = CallCallback(m_uAccumulatedProgress + uProgress);
664  ResetProgressStage();
665  return ret;
666  }
667 
668 protected:
680  virtual bool CallCallback(ZIP_SIZE_TYPE uProgress)
681  {
682  m_uProcessed += uProgress;
683  if (m_pMultiActionsInfo)
684  m_pMultiActionsInfo->OnCallCallback(uProgress);
685  return Callback(uProgress);
686  }
687 
691  void CacheStepSize()
692  {
693  m_iCachedStepSize = GetStepSize();
694  if (m_iCachedStepSize == 0)
695  m_iCachedStepSize = 1;
696  }
697 
705  void ResetProgressStage()
706  {
707  m_iCurrentStep = 1;
708  m_uAccumulatedProgress = 0;
709  }
710 private:
711  CMultiActionsInfo* m_pMultiActionsInfo;
712  void InitMultiActionsInfo()
713  {
714  ReleaseMultiActionsInfo();
715  m_pMultiActionsInfo = new CMultiActionsInfo();
716  }
717  void ReleaseMultiActionsInfo()
718  {
719  if (m_pMultiActionsInfo != NULL)
720  {
721  delete m_pMultiActionsInfo;
722  m_pMultiActionsInfo = NULL;
723  }
724  }
725 
726  int m_iCachedStepSize;
727  int m_iCurrentStep;
728  ZIP_SIZE_TYPE m_uAccumulatedProgress;
729 };
